OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781075106
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch pledges to scrap public
OL,4,Csector equalities law
OL,6,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch has
OL,7,Fsaid her party would scrap the rules
OL,8,Frequiring public bodies such as
OL,9,Fschools and hospitals to promote
OL,10,Fequality when making decisions.
OL,12,FThe Conservatives say it is the first
OL,13,Fstep in their wider plans to "restore
OL,14,Fcommon sense" as Badenoch announced
OL,15,Fthat they would scrap the Public
OL,16,FSector Equality Duty (PSED).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
