CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781075106
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch pledges to scrap public
OL,4,Csector equalities law
OL,6,FThe party leader announced on Tuesday
OL,7,Fthat her party would seek to abolish
OL,8,Fthis duty for teachers, nurses and
OL,9,Fpolice officers to consider protected
OL,10,Fcharacteristics enshrined in equality
OL,11,Flaw as they undertake their day-to-day
OL,12,Fjobs.
OL,14,FThe PSED requires all public sector
OL,15,Fworkers to consider how their work
OL,16,Fmight have an impact on people because
OL,17,Fof their age, sex, sexuality, religion
OL,18,Fand race.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
