OL,3,CKemi Badenoch pledges to scrap public
OL,4,Csector equalities law
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBadenoch's speech comes just a week
OL,12,Fafter a political row broke out over
OL,13,Fwhether the police response to the
OL,14,Fmurder of Henry Nowak in Southampton
OL,15,Flast December was influenced by
OL,16,Fequality law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
