PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781075106
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch pledges to scrap public
OL,4,Csector equalities law
OL,6,F"If authorities weren't concerned that
OL,7,Fblack people were overrepresented in
OL,8,Fmental health events, three people
OL,9,Fwould not have been murdered in
OL,10,FNottingham by a man who should have
OL,11,Fbeen detained under the Mental Health
OL,12,FAct.
OL,14,F"And if authorities hadn't chalked up
OL,15,FAxel Rudakubana's violent behaviour to
OL,16,Fautism, if his head teacher hadn't
OL,17,Fbeen accused of racial stereotyping
OL,18,Fwhen she raised concerns about him
OL,19,Fbringing a knife to school, three
OL,20,Flittle girls might still be here with
OL,21,Fus."
OL,26,@vD@AOU}D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
