OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781075106
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch pledges to scrap public
OL,4,Csector equalities law
OL,6,FShe added: "Public institutions have
OL,7,F"spent so long worrying about
OL,8,Finstitutional racism that they have
OL,9,Fbecome institutionally incompetent".
OL,11,FThe PSED, which applies in England,
OL,12,FScotland and Wales, requires public
OL,13,Fbodies to stop unlawful discrimination.
OL,15,FIt states that authorities should
OL,16,F"advance equality of opportunity
OL,17,Fbetween people who share and people
OL,18,Fwho no share a relevant protected
OL,19,Fcharacteristic".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
