PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781075106
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch pledges to scrap public
OL,4,Csector equalities law
OL,6,FThe government's guidance says the
OL,7,Fduty should be "applied in a
OL,8,Fproportionate way" relating to the
OL,9,Fcircumstances of the case and
OL,10,Forganisations should avoid an "overly
OL,11,Fbureaucratic and burdensome approach".
OL,13,FThe duty was introduced to the
OL,14,FEquality Act in 2010 merging previous
OL,15,Fanti-discrimination laws like the
OL,16,FEqual Pay Act and the Disability
OL,17,FDiscrimination Act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
