PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781075106
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch pledges to scrap public
OL,4,Csector equalities law
OL,6,FScience Secretary Liz Kendall had
OL,7,Fearlier claimed Mrs Badenoch's plans
OL,8,Fto abolish the PSED would "turn the
OL,9,Fclock back".
OL,11,FThe Technology Secretary told ITV News
OL,12,Fthat she is "proud of those
OL,13,Fprotections" and referenced how the
OL,14,Fequality act protects the likes of
OL,15,F"pregnant women from being sacked" and
OL,16,F"older people not been sacked".
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
