FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781075106
OL,3,CKemi Badenoch pledges to scrap public
OL,4,Csector equalities law
OL,6,FShe said that British public services
OL,7,F"will only succeed if they draw on the
OL,8,Ftalents of everybody in the country
OL,9,Fand that is what the Public Service
OL,10,FEquality Duty is all about".
OL,12,FKendall went on to criticise Badenoch
OL,13,Ffor "seeking to divide" on this issue
OL,14,Fand appeal to Reform voters rather
OL,15,Fthan doing the right thing.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
